name: Ode to Sundown
description:
Redefining Monday: As we grow older, there is this gargoyle that loves to hang around our shoulders named anxiety. From the start of our day until sundown, this creature pressures and frames our perspectives— Leading us to blame many things in life such as: responsibilities and unfinished task as the root cause of our energy depletion. Often times, it can also took the joy out of a simple chatter with our peers during office break time. Sad, isn’t it?  

 Monday has become a day we often frowned upon and truthfully, deep inside our hearts, we know that it doesn’t have to stay that way. Just like another day, this too shall pass. 

Altogether with all the good and the bad within. How we want to let it pass though, is an entirely different story, that is up to our own hands to decide.

Artist: Jemala 
Title: Ode to Sundown
Filmed and Edited by Senry Alvin
Format: 1080p MP4 with 320kbps stereo audio 
Duration: 01:16
